== Notes

* Tests needs Ypsilon [1] with an external library (xunit) [2];
  Run `YPSILON_SITELIB="path of (xunit)" make test'.
* For test, this contains IPA Fonts [3], which is redistributed
  under IPA Font License Agreement v1.0.
  See IPAfont00302/Readme_IPAfont00302.txt for detail.

